368
00:21:01,163 --> 00:21:03,163
然後說 ''哦 不 沒關係的''

369
00:21:05,973 --> 00:21:08,063
Put the ship down!

370
00:21:08,143 --> 00:21:10,703
Don't let your personal feelings
get in the way!

371
00:21:24,793 --> 00:21:26,923
Anakin從始到終的問題就是...

372
00:21:26,993 --> 00:21:30,023
